# Normalize all text files to LF in the repository.
# Windows checkouts will still get CRLF in working tree thanks to
# core.autocrlf=true, but Git stores LF, which makes multi-platform
# editing consistent and fixes the mixed CRLF/LF issue from earlier
# Firebase Studio / VS Code / Claude Code sessions.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary files — never touch these
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
